{"tid":456491,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人其實真係無乜志氣","createTime":"2017-11-03T04:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T04:58:31.000Z","uid":56260,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ffcaf696bb27660288129c4e9538650b10d2cfed","tid":456491,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:07:27.000Z","msg":"香港現實生活逼人<br />\n但個個都想追求生活<br />\n上至高官 下至市民<br />\n做官既響大議題上搞勾結、<br />\n同你大玩雙重標準、隻眼開隻眼閉<br />\n做市民既炒樓炒股炒iPhone<br />\n搶平機票、爭埋晒啲咖啡雪糕買一送一<br />\n一句「搵食啫，犯法呀」就大晒咁<br />\n利益當前 香港人真係無乜拒絕既志氣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c14450978e1d0e4a219d3b326634f8588b4b90e3","tid":456491,"uid":117032,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:17:50.000Z","msg":"樓貴租貴食飯貴<br />\n<br />\n人工又唔高，唔炒唔通等死咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06978ebf0bce48a1337ee6037b4ac6e99aa48f87","tid":456491,"uid":45368,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:34:56.000Z","msg":"其實全世界都好似都好難搵到第二個地方好似香港咁<br />\n個個都淨係想撈偏搵快錢<br />\n都算係香港特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfc60a749cefc85bfc7cf2516ffd71ce4384f3db","tid":456491,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:37:32.000Z","msg":"清泉都要食飯"},{"pid":"34776e23f781116368a2ddb3ae07ebe8b6d790de","tid":456491,"uid":56260,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:53:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實全世界都好似都好難搵到第二個地方好似香港咁<br />\n個個都淨係想撈偏搵快錢<br />\n都算係香港特色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n可能有既不過香港應該係唯一已發展地區有咁蓬勃既現象<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20171103/large/1509673537_9479.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171103%2Flarge%2F1509673537_9479.jpg&h=052fd163&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8dabeb21ca8981df5bc780db83527c9d2da8007d","tid":456491,"uid":114275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-03T04:58:31.000Z","msg":"經濟發達但係民智都係未開<br />\n急功近利 無遠見<br />\n上至高官下至平民"}]}